ss=m><span class=title> Ice Comet?</span><hr size=1> My guild leader had four rune of astrals and four runes of frost that he was generous to give to me, I combined all of them with a skill of 148 and 202 int, and now I have 4 Ice comet spells.... I already have a copy of Ice comet for myself, so I'd like to know.... About how much would one of these spells go for...<br>
